snippet.title: VR Skater Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Summer Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
A new gameplay traler for Deficit Games' VR Skater was broadcast during the Summer Showcase, where we saw some cool FGS stickers on the game's customizable decks. VR Skater is kickflipping its way onto PS VR 2 headsets in 2023.
#FutureGamesShow #FGS
